data.description: Store all of your makeup in one place in this beautiful organizer that swivels open so you can see everything at a quick glance. Holds brushes, foundations, eye shadows, 30 lipsticks, blushes, mascara, eye liners and so much more! Measures approximately 14" x 11-1/2" x 8-1/4". Comes in your choice of cherry, white, walnut, oak.
